version_description:
As always, thanks for your feedback! In this release, we’ve improved notifications and made it easier to get more information about rental communities.

Searching and sorting options have also been improved. For example, when you get to the bottom of a search list, just pull up to see more results. We’ve also fixed a few bugs.

Please continue to send your suggestions and report issues to iphonefeedback@zillow.com.

Please continue to send your suggestions and report issues to iphonefeedback@zillow.com.

We have added the ability to save your searches and get notifications about new rental listings that match your search criteria. Your saved searches are also synced across mobile, tablet and desktop, so you can stay informed of new listings from anywhere!

Please continue to send your feedback to iphonefeedback@zillow.com. We appreciate it.

We know in the search for your perfect place, every minute counts! That is why we have added up-to-the-minute listing times to show the number of minutes, hours and days since a new rental listing was posted. We have also added support for the iPhone 6 Plus and updated Settings with new links to make it easier to get help and contact customer support.

Please continue to send your feedback to iphonefeedback@zillow.com. We appreciate it!
